        <p className={`${slider} md:opacity-10 md:mt-96 md:ml-0 ml-12 font-bold flex`}>ABOUT ME</p>
        <p className=' ml-12 md:ml-48 absolute subtitle md:-mt-36  md:text-4xl w-8/12'>Front-end developer who loves to design
